<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_CAS_FaceBody_EyebrowsFacialBodyHair" s="315393">
  <T n="name">0xE9CFF317<!--String: "Eyebrows, Facial & Body Hair"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_EyebrowsFacialAndBodyHair_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d310297428bb6952</T>
      <T n="text">0x868FA2DA<!--String: "Your Sim has more hair than what’s on the top of their head! You can also customize <b><font color='#199C2C'>eyebrows</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>facial hair</font></b>, and <b><font color='#199C2C'>body hair</font></b>. \n\nYou can select a <b><font color='#199C2C'>unique color</font></b> for all these hair categories, or check the Match Hair checkbox to match the color of the hair on your Sim’s head."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_EyebrowsFacialAndBodyHair_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d310297428bb6951</T>
      <T n="text">0x2D6F0CCB<!--String: "Edit your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>eyebrow</font></b> style and color by selecting their head, and then their eyebrows. This will open a menu with different eyebrow styles."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_EyebrowsFacialAndBodyHair_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d310297428bb6950</T>
      <T n="text">0x892E734A<!--String: "To customize the style and color of your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>facial hair</font></b>, select their head, and then the Facial Hair button in the menu. You can sort by category (Beards, Goatees, Mustaches) to make your perfect style easier to find.\n\nOnly Sims with the <b><font color='#199C2C'>male</font></b> gender setting (found in the Identity Panel) can have facial hair."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_EyebrowsFacialAndBodyHair_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d310297428bb6957</T>
      <T n="text">0xB17B16A<!--String: "<b><font color='#199C2C'>Body hair</font></b> comes in four categories; Arm, Torso, Back, and Leg Hair. You can find them by selecting your Sim’s body, and then the Body button. You can select one option in each category, and can select a unique color for each if you wish."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
